<P>
Photo, Leonice Brown gets Crespi off to a fast start as he thwarts Kevin 
Hurley's tackle attempt on his way to a first-quarter touchdown Friday. GEORGE 
WILHELM / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
