FOREIGN RELATIONS -- PLO; WEST BANK (ISRAEL); GAZA STRIP; ARABS -- ISRAEL; 
SHAMIR, YITZHAK; MIDDLE EAST PEACE; EGYPT -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- ISRAEL; 
UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- ISRAEL; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN 
