<P>
Photo, (Southland Edition) USC quarterback Todd Marinovich looks upfield for a 
receiver while two Washington Husky defenders pursue him in the Trojans' 24-16 
victory Oct. 7 at the Coliseum. LORI SHEPLER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
