<TEXT>
<P>
UC Irvine's basketball team takes on Nosso Club Brazil in its second and last 
exhibition game of the season at 7:30 tonight in the Bren Center. 
</P>
<P>
Irvine is coming off a 99-96 victory over High Five America Wednesday. Rod 
Palmer, Justin Anderson and Jeff Herdman each scored 18 points. 
