<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY EARNINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
EIP Microwave Inc.: The Newport Beach-based microwave test and measurement 
instrument manufacturer earned net income of $771,000 for the fiscal year ended 
Sept. 30, contrasted with a loss of $1.6 million for fiscal 1988. The current 
year's results reflect a gain of $748,000 from an accounting change. Sales 
increased 22%, to $13.8 million from $11.3 million. Fourth-quarter net income 
totaled $293,000, 66% higher than the $177,000 posted a year ago. Sales rose 
5%, to $3.6 million from $3.4 million. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column; Corporate Earnings 
</P>
