</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Airport flights -- A story Friday incorrectly stated the number of new daily 
flights to be awarded airlines serving John Wayne Airport beginning next April. 
The correct number of additional flights is 18, which will increase the total 
number of average daily flights from 55 to 73. 
</P>
